claim: Queen Victoria was alive during the 1870s.
premise_source_doc_sentence: According to the English merchant Edward Lucett , the news of the infant 's death arrived by June 21 , 1845 ; however , a letter dated to November 24 of the same year , written to the Pritchard family of England from Pomare 's children , included Victoria 's name along with her siblings ' , which may indicate that she was still alive .
